  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个状态图，描述从开发到最终应用部署的完整流程。起点是开发者拿到需求，终点是应用上线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Developer",
        "Application"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，那开发者之后是直接对接基础设施，还是中间还有别的环节？比如配置管理之类的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure",
        "configMap"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "开发者需要同时关心基础设施和配置。基础设施是硬件资源，configMap是我们用来管理应用配置的。这两块是并行的，开发者都要打交道。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure",
        "configMap"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把开发者指向基础设施和configMap的两条连线加上。那基础设施和configMap之间有关系吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure",
        "configMap"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有的，基础设施要读取configMap里的配置才能正确初始化。然后configMap的配置最终要同步到Kubernetes集群里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infrastructure",
        "configMap",
        "Kubernetes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "所以是基础设施指向configMap，configMap再指向Kubernetes，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infrastructure",
        "configMap",
        "Kubernetes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，最后Kubernetes部署完，应用就运行起来了，流程结束。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Kubernetes",
        "Application",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。整个流程是：开发者启动，同时对接基础设施和配置，基础设施依赖配置，配置进入Kubernetes，最后应用上线。你看看还有要调整的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
